tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
I was recommended to visit Dr. Chethan by a friend who was treated previously by him. Outstanding professionalism and pain free treatment. I really appreciated the amount of time Doctor spent to explain the procedure to me and he was very patient with me as I asked him doubts about what I didn‚Äôt understand. 
The positive and friendly approach he had made me feel very comfortable as it was my first visit to dentist. 
I was very scared of pain during treatment but was pleasantly surprised to see 0 pain and I was happy to see how smoothly my treatment went through. 
Doctor explained my treatment plan to me initially and throughout the process and made sure I‚Äôm comfortable throughout. And the final result was outstanding 
10/10 for the quality of treatment and professionalism
10/10 for his friendly nature and comforting presence

Highly recommend Dr. Chethan for any and every dental treatment, with no doubt whatsoever. 

Thank you doctor for making my first experience make my fear of dental treatments completely 0, and I‚Äôm looking forward to having you as our family dentist in the years to come as well.
Very professional,  and finished the job quicker than expected. Took an appointment the same morning and got for the same day.
Procedure charges are exorbitant high. Take complete charges details before entering  lying on dental table .

Excellent team... I am very happy for getting good doctor team in pranam Dental hospital. I enquired about my root canal treatment with many dentist but they were saying different things and cost of treatment will be more.but I saw good reviews about pranam Dental Hospital especially about Dr. Chethan and Dr. Abhishek, then thought of visiting there. When I visited pranam dental clinic doctors explained what is my exact problem and within 3 to 4 days they completed my root canal treatment . Dr chethan, Dr abhishek and their team is very good and very quick  in giving the treatment, first time I saw a dentist giving the treatment late night till 11pm it shows their passion of giving treatment to their patients. Whoever want treatment for dental problems visit to pranam dental hospital where u will get good team of doctors with less budget.

Dr. Chethan put a Lava 3M dental crown in October 2020 with assured 15 Years warranty which can be claimed anywhere in India. Since then the crown came off my tooth at last 3-4 times. I got it fixed from multiple doctors. Finally, the crown broke 1 week back when I am in Chandigarh. I have been trying to contact multiple labs in Chandigarh and no one is willing to give the warranty. I have been contacting the doctor and he is also not helping. Now I am stuck with a broken tooth even after spending Rs. 20,000 on my treatment. **** * *** *** *** ********* *************** *********. I don't understand what to do now.
